      "content": "the heat and walking isn't even touching it. i'm honestly desperate here. i checked my cabinet and i have some extra strength ibuprofen and strength aspirin. if i took like another 800mg of the ibuprofen now it would be my third dose today but it's better than lying here in pain. is that actually dangerous or is it just a guideline? i feel like i can handle it if it means i can actually sleep.",
