      "content": "i get the risks but i feel like i know my body and i've taken stuff like this before. i just need a solution right now. if i can't take more ibuprofen, what's the absolute most i can take in a day to actually get some relief? like, what's the real limit before it's actually an emergency? just tell me the max so i can decide how to handle this.",
